{
  "stem": "11272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found another plumber's apprentice job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I stayed there till I was about 15.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I came back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by that time, all hell broke loose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jews not only were attacked, and, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] done everything that you could do wrong-- or, or, or the damage to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were being-- we were being robbed and attacked constantly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was about Passover time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was the last day of Passover, 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a knock on the door-- excuse me, a week or so before Passover.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was another knock on the door at 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somebody tried to come and arrest my father and take him away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And somehow Rosalyn saw it, my sister, Rosalyn, who was the youngest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she cried, and she screamed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And finally, the rest of us arrived, the rest of the brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we managed to get rid of that guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They tried to take over my father's business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- but this was about the last day of Passover when they knocked on our door.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they gave us five minutes to pack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, you know, they kept on telling us, look, we're going to take you away from these local, Jew-hating anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We're going to relocate you to Germany where we're going to give you jobs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you're going to be away from constant harassment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and you'll be able to get food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At worst, you didn't get ration coupons here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You couldn't even buy food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this went on till-- to a point where we were almost resigned to the fact that, look, they don't take us away.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
